Usage: refinePlace [-help] [-area {lx ly ux uy}] [-eco {true|false}]
                   [-inst <value>] [-wire_length_reclaim {true|false}]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-area {lx ly ux uy}                   # specify refinePlace area in um
                                      # (box, default={0 0 0 0})
-eco {true|false}                     # activate ECO mode for post-route design
                                      # (bool, default=false)
-inst <value>                         # specify a list of instances for
                                      # refinePlace to legalizes only
                                      # (string, default="")
-wire_length_reclaim {true|false}     # activate wire length reclaim mode
                                      # (bool, default=false)